comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position and briefly places his hands to Russell's (LAL) body.
Russell (LAL) moves underneath Lillard (MIL) as he is airborne, initiating contact to his lower body that affects his ability  to return to the floor during the jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in Dinwiddie's (LAL) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Davis (LAL) makes incidental contact to Connaughton's (MIL) lower body as he contests the shot attempt near the basket.
Hachimura (LAL) establishes himself in Connaughton's (MIL) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in Dinwiddie's (LAL) path when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Dinwiddie (LAL) briefly places his hand to Lillard's (MIL) body and slightly extends his arm during the drive, which does not affect Lillard's SQBR.
The ball is last touched by Russell (LAL) prior to it going out of bounds.
Lillard (MIL) is in a legally obtained position in Davis' (LAL) path when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Replay review of the foul called on Dinwiddie (LAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Dinwiddie places a forearm against Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side, but the contact is marginal.
Lillard (MIL) is not established in a legal guarding position in Russell's (LAL) path at the time of the contact, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) collapses his arms as he absorbs the incoming contact from Davis (LAL) during the screen.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in Reddish's (LAL) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Davis (LAL) briefly places a hand on Lillard's (MIL) hip during his drive to the basket but the contact does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (LAL) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Russell (LAL) releases from Lillard (MIL) as he slightly extends his arm during the drive, but does not dislodge Lillard from his defensive position.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in Reddish's (LAL) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Dinwiddie (MIL) cleanly blocks Lillard's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (LAL) extends his leg out and kicks the ball with his foot.
The game clock expires prior to the ball going out of bounds.
